      <title><![CDATA[Swift Functions]]></title>
      <url>/2017/06/27/Swift%20Functions/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Functions"><a href="#Functions" class="headerlink" title="Functions"></a>Functions</h1><h2 id="函数基本形式"><a href="#函数基本形式" class="headerlink" title="函数基本形式"></a>函数基本形式</h2><p><code>(parameter types) -&gt; return type</code></p>
<p>例如:</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">() -&gt; Void</div><div class="line">(String, [String]) -&gt; String?</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="无返回值的函数"><a href="#无返回值的函数" class="headerlink" title="无返回值的函数"></a>无返回值的函数</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">func sendMessage(_ message: String, to recipient: String, shouting: Bool = false) &#123;</div><div class="line">    var message = &quot;\(message), \(recipient)!&quot;</div><div class="line">    if shouting &#123;</div><div class="line">        message = message.uppercased()</div><div class="line">    &#125;</div><div class="line">    print(message)</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">//调用方法</div><div class="line">sendMessage(&quot;See you at the Bash&quot;, to: &quot;Morgan&quot;)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="有参有返回值"><a href="#有参有返回值" class="headerlink" title="有参有返回值"></a>有参有返回值</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">//注意返回值后面的问号</div><div class="line">func firstString(havingPrefix prefix: String,in strings: [String]) -&gt; String? &#123;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">    for string in strings &#123;</div><div class="line">        if string.hasPrefix(prefix) &#123;</div><div class="line">            return string</div><div class="line">        &#125;</div><div class="line">    &#125;</div><div class="line">    return nil</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">//调用方法</div><div class="line">firstString(havingPrefix: &quot;a&quot;, in: [&quot;a123&quot;,&quot;b123&quot;])</div><div class="line">//使用方法</div><div class="line">if let a = firstString(havingPrefix: &quot;a&quot;, in: [&quot;a123&quot;,&quot;b123&quot;]) &#123;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">&#125; else &#123;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>参数中带有函数</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div><div class="line">35</div><div class="line">36</div><div class="line">37</div><div class="line">38</div><div class="line">39</div><div class="line">40</div><div class="line">41</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">func filterInts(_ numbers: [Int], _ includeNumber: (Int) -&gt; Bool) -&gt; [Int] &#123;</div><div class="line">    var result: [Int] = []</div><div class="line">    for number in numbers &#123;</div><div class="line">        if includeNumber(number) &#123;</div><div class="line">            result.append(number)</div><div class="line">        &#125;</div><div class="line">    &#125;</div><div class="line">    return result</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">let array = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7]</div><div class="line">func double(_ number: Int) -&gt; Bool&#123;</div><div class="line">    return number % 2 == 0</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">//调用方法1</div><div class="line">*注意这个位置调用double函数后面没有括号,</div><div class="line">因为他不是现在调用,</div><div class="line">而是稍晚一些在函数中调用*</div><div class="line">let a = filterInts(array, double)</div><div class="line">//调用方法2(闭包表达式,完全形式)</div><div class="line">let a = filterInts(array) &#123; (number : Int) -&gt; Bool in</div><div class="line">    return number % 2 == 0</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">//调用方法3</div><div class="line">let a = filterInts(array) &#123; number in</div><div class="line">    return number % 2 == 0</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">//调用方法4</div><div class="line">let a = filterInts(array) &#123; number in</div><div class="line">   number % 2 == 0</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">//调用方法5</div><div class="line">*Swfit提供暗示变量名,</div><div class="line">变量可以使用$0,$1,$2..</div><div class="line">数字代表第几个变量</div><div class="line">*</div><div class="line">let a = filterInts(array) &#123; $0 % 2 == 0&#125;</div><div class="line">//调用方法7 (尾随闭包)</div><div class="line">*当闭包是最后一个参数时,可以使用尾随闭包</div><div class="line">*</div><div class="line">let a = filterInts(array)&#123;$0 % 2 == 0&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="泛型函数"><a href="#泛型函数" class="headerlink" title="泛型函数"></a>泛型函数</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">func filter&lt;Element&gt;(_ source: [Element], _ includeElement: (Element) -&gt; Bool) -&gt; [Element] &#123;</div><div class="line">    var result: [Element] = []</div><div class="line">    for item in source &#123;</div><div class="line">        if includeElement(item) &#123;</div><div class="line">            result.append(item)</div><div class="line">        &#125;</div><div class="line">    &#125;</div><div class="line">    return result</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">//调用方法1</div><div class="line">let b = filter(array) &#123; (number) -&gt; Bool in</div><div class="line">   return number % 2 == 0</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">print(b)</div><div class="line">//调用方法2</div><div class="line">let c = filter([&quot;a&quot;,&quot;bb&quot;,&quot;ccc&quot;,&quot;dddd&quot;]) &#123;</div><div class="line">    str in str.characters.count &gt; 2</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">print(c)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="多个函数同时调用"><a href="#多个函数同时调用" class="headerlink" title="多个函数同时调用"></a>多个函数同时调用</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">let d = [&quot;a&quot;,&quot;bb&quot;,&quot;ccc&quot;,&quot;dddd&quot;].filter&#123; $0.characters.count &gt; 2&#125;</div><div class="line">        .map &#123;$0.uppercased()&#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">print(d)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
      
        
    </entry>
    
    <entry>
      <title><![CDATA[Swift Base]]></title>
      <url>/2017/06/27/Swift%20Base/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Swift-Base"><a href="#Swift-Base" class="headerlink" title="Swift Base"></a>Swift Base</h1><h2 id="let"><a href="#let" class="headerlink" title="let"></a>let</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">let language = &quot;swift&quot;</div><div class="line">let num: Int = 1</div><div class="line">let isTrue = true</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="var"><a href="#var" class="headerlink" title="var"></a>var</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">var str = &quot;Hello, playground&quot;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>对变量进行操作</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">str = str + str</div><div class="line">str = &quot;\(str)\(str)&quot;</div><div class="line">str = &quot;\(str.characters.count)&quot;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="Array"><a href="#Array" class="headerlink" title="Array"></a>Array</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">let names = [&quot;Lily&quot;, &quot;Santiago&quot;, &quot;Justyn&quot;, &quot;Aadya&quot;] //推荐</div><div class="line">let names: [String] = [&quot;Lily&quot;, &quot;Santiago&quot;, &quot;Justyn&quot;, &quot;Aadya&quot;]</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="Modifying-an-Array"><a href="#Modifying-an-Array" class="headerlink" title="Modifying an Array"></a>Modifying an Array</h2><h3 id="add"><a href="#add" class="headerlink" title="add"></a>add</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">var array = [&quot;a&quot;, &quot;b&quot;, &quot;c&quot;]</div><div class="line">array.append(&quot;d&quot;) //增加</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="remove"><a href="#remove" class="headerlink" title="remove"></a>remove</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">array.remove(at: 1)</div><div class="line">array.removeAll()</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="update"><a href="#update" class="headerlink" title="update"></a>update</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">array[0] = &quot;e&quot;</div><div class="line">array[2...3] = [&quot;x&quot;, &quot;y&quot;]</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="Dictionary"><a href="#Dictionary" class="headerlink" title="Dictionary"></a>Dictionary</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">let ages = [&quot;Mohsen&quot;: 17, &quot;Amy&quot;: 40, &quot;Graham&quot;: 5]</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="Modifying-an-dictionary"><a href="#Modifying-an-dictionary" class="headerlink" title="Modifying an dictionary"></a>Modifying an dictionary</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">let b: Int? = ages[&quot;d&quot;]</div><div class="line">if b == nil&#123;</div><div class="line">    print(&quot;It&apos;s nil&quot;)</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>等价于</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">//推荐</div><div class="line">if let c = ages[&quot;Amy&quot;] &#123;</div><div class="line">    print(&quot;name is \(c)&quot;)</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="Loops"><a href="#Loops" class="headerlink" title="Loops"></a>Loops</h2><h3 id="While-amp-Repeat-While"><a href="#While-amp-Repeat-While" class="headerlink" title="While &amp; Repeat-While"></a>While &amp; Repeat-While</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">while !endOfFile &#123;</div><div class="line"> readLine()</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">repeat &#123;</div><div class="line"> performTask()</div><div class="line">&#125; while tasksRemaining &gt; 0</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="For-In"><a href="#For-In" class="headerlink" title="For-In"></a>For-In</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">let dogString = &quot;Dog⁈🐶&quot;</div><div class="line">for character in dogString.characters &#123;</div><div class="line">   print(character)</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">for number in 1...5 &#123;</div><div class="line">   print(&quot;\(number) times 4 is \(number * 4)&quot;)</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">let results = [7, 52, 9, 33, 6, 12, 86, 4, 22, 18, 3]</div><div class="line">let maxResultCount = 5</div><div class="line">for index in 0..&lt;maxResultCount &#123;</div><div class="line">   print(&quot;Result \(index) is \(results[index])&quot;)</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">for name in [&quot;Lily&quot;, &quot;Santiago&quot;, &quot;Justyn&quot;, &quot;Aadya&quot;] &#123;</div><div class="line">   print(&quot;Hello, \(name)!&quot;)</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">let ages = [&quot;Mohsen&quot;: 17, &quot;Amy&quot;: 40, &quot;Graham&quot;: 5]</div><div class="line">for (name, age) in ages &#123;</div><div class="line">   print(&quot;\(name) is \(age) years old&quot;)</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="if"><a href="#if" class="headerlink" title="if"></a>if</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">let age = 32</div><div class="line">if age == 1 &#123;</div><div class="line"> print(&quot;Happy first birthday!&quot;)</div><div class="line">&#125; else if age == 40 &#123;</div><div class="line"> print(&quot;Happy 40th birthday!&quot;)</div><div class="line">&#125; else &#123;</div><div class="line"> print(&quot;no&quot;)</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="switch"><a href="#switch" class="headerlink" title="switch"></a>switch</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">let age = 40</div><div class="line">switch age &#123;</div><div class="line">case 1:</div><div class="line">    print(&quot;Happy first birthday!&quot;)</div><div class="line">case 13...19:</div><div class="line">    print(&quot;Happy birthday, teenager!&quot;)</div><div class="line">case let decade where decade % 10 == 0:</div><div class="line">    print(&quot;Happy significant \(decade)th birthday!&quot;)</div><div class="line">default</div><div class="line">    print(&quot;no&quot;)</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">let userName = &quot;admian&quot;</div><div class="line">let passwordIsValid = true</div><div class="line">switch (userName, passwordIsValid) &#123;</div><div class="line">case (&quot;admin&quot;, true):</div><div class="line">    print(&quot;Welcome back, administrator!&quot;)</div><div class="line">case (&quot;guest&quot;, _):</div><div class="line">    print(&quot;Guests are not allowed in this restricted area.&quot;)</div><div class="line">case (_, let isValid):</div><div class="line">    print(isValid ? &quot;Welcome to the restricted area!&quot; : &quot;ACCESS DENIED.&quot;)</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
      
        
    </entry>
    
    <entry>
      <title><![CDATA[CocoaPods的各种姿势（基础篇）]]></title>
      <url>/2016/10/31/CocoaPods%E7%9A%84%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E5%A7%BF%E5%8A%BF%EF%BC%88%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%AF%87%EF%BC%89/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="CocoaPods的各种姿势（基础篇）"><a href="#CocoaPods的各种姿势（基础篇）" class="headerlink" title="CocoaPods的各种姿势（基础篇）"></a>CocoaPods的各种姿势（基础篇）</h1><h2 id="概况"><a href="#概况" class="headerlink" title="概况"></a>概况</h2><p>​    CocoaPods是一个十分强大的iOS依赖管理工具，为我们提供便捷的管理第三方库的方式。在项目实际开发过程中，免不了使用各种第三方的开源类库、集成第三方的SDK，如AFNetWorking、FMDB等等，我们可以把这些公共组件交给它去管理。</p>
<p>​    如果你之前有了解java的Maven或者nodejs的npm，那么你能更轻易的了解CocoaPods这个工具。</p>
<h2 id="安装CocoaPods"><a href="#安装CocoaPods" class="headerlink" title="安装CocoaPods"></a>安装CocoaPods</h2><p>在 OS X 下安装CocoaPods十分简单，只需要打开terminal输入如下命令：</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ sudo gem install cocoapods</div><div class="line">$ pod setup</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>CocoaPods在<a href="https://rubygems.org/托管，所以在国内下载很慢，我们需要替换我们能访问到的源，如果你已经是墙外用户可以忽略下面步骤：" target="_blank" rel="external">https://rubygems.org/托管，所以在国内下载很慢，我们需要替换我们能访问到的源，如果你已经是墙外用户可以忽略下面步骤：</a></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ gem sources --add https://gems.ruby-china.org/ --remove https://rubygems.org/</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="使用CocoaPods的镜像索引"><a href="#使用CocoaPods的镜像索引" class="headerlink" title="使用CocoaPods的镜像索引"></a>使用CocoaPods的镜像索引</h3><p>​    如果pod setup会等比较久，如果太长时间没有反应，可以尝试使用CocoaPods的镜像索引来提高下载速度。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ pod repo remove master</div><div class="line">$ pod repo add master https://gitcafe.com/akuandev/Specs.git</div><div class="line">$ pod repo update</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="在一个Xcode工程下使用CocoaPods"><a href="#在一个Xcode工程下使用CocoaPods" class="headerlink" title="在一个Xcode工程下使用CocoaPods"></a>在一个Xcode工程下使用CocoaPods</h2><ul>
<li><p>打开Terminal，<code>$ cd</code> 到 Xcode 工程根目录。</p>
</li>
<li><p>使用<code>$ pod init</code>命令创建Podfile文件。</p>
</li>
<li><p>打开Podfile，首先指定支持的平台和版本，例如：</p>
<blockquote>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&gt; platform :ios, &apos;9.0&apos;</div><div class="line">&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</blockquote>
</li>
<li><p>新的版本中需要指定 Xcode target，例如：</p>
<blockquote>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&gt; target &apos;MyApp&apos; do</div><div class="line">&gt;   pod &apos;AFNetworking&apos;</div><div class="line">&gt; end</div><div class="line">&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</blockquote>
</li>
<li><p>这样一个Podfile文件就写好了，保存并执行<code>$ pod install</code>命令。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>这时候Xcode根目录会生成一个.xcworkspace的文件，指定的库就集成好了。</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="pod-install-amp-pod-update区别"><a href="#pod-install-amp-pod-update区别" class="headerlink" title="pod install &amp; pod update区别"></a>pod install &amp; pod update区别</h2><p>刚接触 CocoaPods 的开发者会经常分不清这两者的区别。</p>
<ul>
<li><p>pod install：</p>
<blockquote>
<ul>
<li>在项目安装新的pod中使用，会安装指定的第三方库。</li>
<li>新添加库，pod install会对曾经添加的库默认使用现有的版本，无需下载，对于新添加的库会下载安装。耗时短。</li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
</li>
<li><p>pod update：</p>
<blockquote>
<ul>
<li>使用pod update会对所有的库进行版本校验，如果发现更新则下载更新。耗时长。</li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="管理Pods依赖库版本"><a href="#管理Pods依赖库版本" class="headerlink" title="管理Pods依赖库版本"></a>管理Pods依赖库版本</h2><p>通过下面的方式，可以很轻易的对库的版本进行管理：</p>
<ul>
<li>pod ‘AFNetworking’ //不显式指定依赖库版本，表示每次都获取最新版本</li>
<li>pod ‘AFNetworking’, ‘2.0’ //只使用2.0版本</li>
<li>pod ‘AFNetworking’, ‘&gt; 2.0’ //使用大于2.0的版本</li>
<li>pod ‘AFNetworking’, ‘&gt;= 2.0’ //使用大于或等于2.0的版本</li>
<li>pod ‘AFNetworking’, ‘&lt; 2.0’ //使用小于2.0的版本</li>
<li>pod ‘AFNetworking’, ‘&lt;= 2.0’ //使用小于或等于2.0的版本</li>
<li>pod ‘AFNetworking’, ‘~&gt; 0.1.2’ //使用大于等于0.1.2但小于0.2的版本</li>
<li>pod ‘AFNetworking’, ‘~&gt; 0.1’ //使用大于等于0.1但小于1.0的版本</li>
<li>pod ‘AFNetworking’, ‘~&gt; 0’ //使用大于0的版本，和什么都不写效果相同</li>
</ul>
]]></content>
      
        
    </entry>
    
    <entry>
      <title><![CDATA[CocoaPods 配置]]></title>
      <url>/2016/09/05/CocoaPods%20%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>#CocoaPods 配置</p>
<p>##一.CocoaPods   安装</p>
<p>1.<code>gem sources --remove https://rubygems.org/</code></p>
<p>如果出现:</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">ERROR:  While executing gem ... (Errno::EACCES)</div><div class="line">    Permission denied - /Users/chenyuanyuan/.gemrc</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>使用<code>sudo</code> 试一次</p>
<p>2.<code>gem sources -a http://ruby.taobao.org/</code></p>
<p>3.<code>gem sources -l</code></p>
<p>4.<code>sudo gem install cocoapods</code></p>
<p>(可以使用<code>cd ~/.cocoapods</code>目录下<br>使用<code>du -sh *</code>来查看下载进度)</p>
<p>5.<code>pod setup</code></p>
<p>注意:如果出现</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">[!] /usr/bin/git clone &apos;https://github.com/CocoaPods/Specs.git&apos; master --depth=1</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">xcrun: error: active developer path (&quot;/Users/vision/Desktop/Xcode.app/Contents/Developer&quot;) does not exist, use xcode-select to change</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>使用:<br><code>sudo xcode-select -switch /Applications/Xcode.app/Contents/Developer</code> (Xcode.app为名字)</p>
<p>##二. 使用CocoaPods的镜像索引<br>1.<code>pod repo remove master</code></p>
<p>2.<code>pod repo add master https://gitcafe.com/akuandev/Specs.git</code></p>
<p>3.<code>pod repo update</code></p>
<p>或者将上网址替换:<code>https://git.oschina.net/akuandev/Specs.git</code></p>
<p>##三.使用CocoaPods<br>新建一个名字为 <code>Podfile</code></p>
<p>可以使用 <code>touch Podfile</code></p>
<p>例如:安装SBJson</p>
<p>1.在<code>Podfile</code>中写入</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">platform :ios</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">pod &apos;SBJson&apos;, &apos;~&gt; 4.0.1’</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>使用命令 <code>pod install</code></p>
<p>##四:使用CocoaPods错误处理<br>错误1:</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">[!] The platform of the target `Pods` (iOS 4.3) is not compatible with `SBJson (4.0.1)` which has a minimum requirement of iOS 5.0 - OS X 10.7.</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>解决方法:改为  <code>platform :ios, ‘8.0’</code></p>
<p>错误2: </p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">fatal: Not a git repository (or any of the parent directories): .git</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>解决方法: 使用命令 <code>git init</code></p>
<p>错误3:</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">[!] Invalid `Podfile` file: incompatible character encodings: UTF-8 and ASCII-8BIT. Updating CocoaPods might fix the issue.</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>查看编码,执行命令<br><code>locale</code></p>
<p>执行命令后出现</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">LANG=&quot;zh_CN.UTF-8&quot;</div><div class="line">LC_COLLATE=&quot;zh_CN.UTF-8&quot;</div><div class="line">LC_CTYPE=&quot;zh_CN.UTF-8&quot;</div><div class="line">LC_MESSAGES=&quot;zh_CN.UTF-8&quot;</div><div class="line">LC_MONETARY=&quot;zh_CN.UTF-8&quot;</div><div class="line">LC_NUMERIC=&quot;zh_CN.UTF-8&quot;</div><div class="line">LC_TIME=&quot;zh_CN.UTF-8&quot;</div><div class="line">LC_ALL=</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>发现都是zh，强制设置一下,命令:</p>
<p><code>export LC_ALL=en_US.UTF-8</code></p>
<p><code>export LANG=en_US.UTF-8</code></p>
<p>再检查一下</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">LANG=&quot;en_US.UTF-8&quot;</div><div class="line">LC_COLLATE=&quot;en_US.UTF-8&quot;</div><div class="line">LC_CTYPE=&quot;en_US.UTF-8&quot;</div><div class="line">LC_MESSAGES=&quot;en_US.UTF-8&quot;</div><div class="line">LC_MONETARY=&quot;en_US.UTF-8&quot;</div><div class="line">LC_NUMERIC=&quot;en_US.UTF-8&quot;</div><div class="line">LC_TIME=&quot;en_US.UTF-8&quot;</div><div class="line">LC_ALL=&quot;en_US.UTF-8&quot;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>好像好了，继续pod install吧</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">[!] Invalid `Podfile` file: incompatible character encodings: UTF-8 and ASCII-8BIT. Updating CocoaPods might fix the issue.</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>问题依然<br>把所有可能的配置都试一遍<br><code>gem install rails</code></p>
<p>然后<br><code>gem install rdoc</code></p>
<p>然后<br><code>gem install nokogiri --no-ri --no-rdoc</code></p>
<p>这些都设置完一般不会出现问题了，再有问题，可能是文本录入的问题</p>
<p>OK 如果你还有问题 试试下面的 :</p>
<p><code>打开系统偏好设置 - 键盘 - 文本</code></p>
<p>改成上面的样式<br> ok如果你还有问题 那就再终端上敲吧</p>
<p><code>vim Podfile</code><br>按 <code>i</code>输入 </p>
<p>输入结束后 </p>
<p>按<code>esc+ shift+;</code>输入<code>wq</code> 回车<br>ok</p>
<p>如果你还有问题 那别玩iOS了 玩别的去吧!(玩笑)</p>
]]></content>
      
        
